    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its composure with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system providing distinct damping profiles. Maintenance is up to date, including recent throttle actuator service and a full synthetic oil change. The hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering remains sharp, and the subframe bushings are in solid condition. This is a robust, driver-spec example of BMW M's last atmospheric V8.",
      "price": 34500.0,
