    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday practicality. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows only light bolster wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a fresh oil service. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It handles beautifully on the highway with no unusual noises or vibrations. This is a solid, reliable choice for a buyer seeking a high-quality pre-owned vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
